-- Delta denies merger talks with UAL
-- 
-- Wed Nov 14, 2007 3:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/14/us-delta-ual-denial-idUSWEN258820071114

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Delta Air Lines Inc ( DAL.N ) said on Wednesday that there were no ongoing talks to merge with United Airlines parent UAL Corp UAUA.O. 

 "There have been no talks with United regarding any type of consolidation transaction and there are no such ongoing discussions," Chief Executive Richard Anderson said in a statement. Earlier on Wednesday, the Associated Press had reported that the United and Delta were discussing a possible deal. (Reporting by  Chris Reiter ; Editing by  Leslie Gevirtz )